精准度的同时，我们也在探索其他方法，如制作鲜奶冰淇淋、鲜奶茶等，在保障鲜度前提下减少浪费。现制“鲜奶冰淇淋”的原料主要为保质期内的鲜奶，售价2元/支；所用的鲜奶均为低温冷藏，请大家放心。 由于每日未售出的日日鲜牛奶不多，该冰淇淋为限量销售。经过前期测试，目前鲜奶冰淇淋已在上海、杭州、北京、广州、深圳、重庆的32家门店上线；如有建议或意见，欢迎随时向小二反馈。 由此给大家带来的误会，我们深感抱歉，也感谢大家的理解与体谅。夏天要到了，冰淇淋很好吃；做冰淇淋的不只可以用奶浆、奶粉，也可以用鲜奶。"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyvmW2uy3nddJEAMaCDYzNzk3Mzk0IIr3noQGMAw41gJACXIJNDU2ODI3Nzc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"567 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-f2b76c82b79e63d887dfbadf1b34d392_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1619702322.2200136","card_id":"Q_444218811","target":{"id":444218811,"title":"1+0.1+0.01+0.001+0.0001... 一直下去会在实际中到达 2 吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/444218811","type":"question","created":1613195597,"answer_count":1569,"follower_count":3015,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,2253],"comment_count":231,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIyvmW2uy3nddJEAMaCDYwOTkzODU3IM3SnYEGMOcBOMcXQApyCTQ0NDIxODgxMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"531 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7b4d66ec3f563d9b4f38bc9f2443d1bf_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1619702322.2204294","card_id":"Q_456933930","target":{"id":456933930,"title":"印度男子杀害感染新冠妻子后跳楼自尽，大环境下普通人的生活有多无力？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/456933930","type":"question","created":1619568562,"answer_count":224,"follower_count":1599,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2025,4311,4621,583143,583976],"comment_count":31,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"新冠疫情近乎失控，一幕幕惨剧正在印度国内不断上演。据印度报业托拉斯（PTI）26日报道，当地警方表示，在巴特那某地，一名男子周一用利器杀害了自己感染新冠病毒的妻子后，跳楼自