改善吗？我管不住它啊！真的怕哪天晚上被压的一个没呼吸上来就过去了（经常被压醒，然后把它推下去又上来）"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyvmW2uy3nddJEAMaCDYzNjM2MTAxIM7wiIQGMBA41wNAEXIJNDU2MTAyNTg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"252 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5d4fb09ed974526bddcbe9af73e89440_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1619702322.2240891","card_id":"Q_40568999","target":{"id":40568999,"title":"《龙族》里诺诺的真实身份到底是谁？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/40568999","type":"question","created":1455940211,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":246,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[38825,98713],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"龙族三里诺诺到底去了哪？整整一部都没提到她，为什么龙四里奥丁遇见诺诺会说「你终于来了。」 奥丁的死敌是黑王，它一直在等着的莫非就是黑王诺诺？ 还有学长到底是什么身份？肯德基？副校长的小弟？有多大的能力？"},"attached_info":"Cj0IyvmW2uy3nddJEAMaBzg0MzQ2NTgg88SftgUwBTj2AUAScgg0MDU2ODk5OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"247 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-5c5c862e2b4d0c56170e8e189b1decc0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1619702322.2245498","card_id":"Q_413382261","target":{"id":413382261,"title":"贾府败落后，李纨为什么不肯救贾家那一干落难的人？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/413382261","type":"question","created":1597087421,"answer_count":23,"follower_count":130,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[7246,86198,156311,193143,599514],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"以前怎么看不出她是这么冷血的人？"},"attached_info":"Cj8IyvmW2uy3nddJEAMaCDU0MTM5ODg4IL29xvkFMAE4ggFAE3IJNDEzMzgyMjYxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"247 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic